Publication
Teenage Renaissance! David, written and illustrated by Yushin Kuroki, was serialized in Shueisha's  manga magazine Weekly Shōnen Jump from September 15, 2018, to May 27, 2019. Shueisha collected its chapters in four  volumes, released from January 4 to July 4, 2019.
Viz Media published the series' first three chapters for its "Jump Start" initiative. Shueisha simultaneously published the manga in English on its Manga Plus online platform.
